### 8.7 Function Types

#### Function Parameter Types

```typescript
// Basic function
function greet(name: string): string {
  return `Hello, ${name}!`;
}

// Optional parameters
function buildUser(
  name: string,
  email: string,
  age?: number  // Optional
): User {
